description: We have many tools in web to generate random number from the user input. when user provides minimum and maximum number these tools will create random number. This skill provides the random number by asking the maximum number for the random generator. currently we are restricting the maximum number to 1000 for the simplicity but there should not be any restriction based on the user input.
name: Randomgenerator
shortDescription: This skill generate random number from the maximum number user provided.
